Function Reference/create empty blog « WordPress Codex
-----------

Creates a new, empty blog.

Usage
-----

` <?php create_empty_blog( $domain, $path, $weblog_title, $site_id ) ?> `

Parameters
----------

 `$domain` 
:   ([*string*](/How_to_Pass_Tag_Parameters#String "How to Pass Tag Parameters"))
    (*required*) Domain name for blog.
    Default: *None*

 `$path` 
:   ([*string*](/How_to_Pass_Tag_Parameters#String "How to Pass Tag Parameters"))
    (*required*) Path to the blog.
    Default: *None*

 `$weblog_title` 
:   ([*string*](/How_to_Pass_Tag_Parameters#String "How to Pass Tag Parameters"))
    (*required*) Title for blog.
    Default: *None*

 `$site_id` 
:   ([*int*](/How_to_Pass_Tag_Parameters#Int "How to Pass Tag Parameters"))
    (*optional*) Site ID, if running multiple networks.
    Default: 1

Returns
-------

 `` `(integer)`{style="color:gray"} 
:   The ID of the newly created blog

Examples
--------

Notes
-----

Change Log
----------

Since: [3.0.0](/Version_3.0 "Version 3.0")

Source File
-----------

`create_empty_blog()` is located in `wp-includes/ms-functions.php`

